testsuite.name: au.org.ala.ecodata.ManagementUnitControllerSpec

testcase.name: A user can retrieve a list of MUs they have a role assigned to
The management unit controller can request a geojson FeatureCollection containing all of the management unit sites
The management unit controller can request a geojson FeatureCollection containing sites for specific management units
Not supplying an id to the update method will create a management unit
Extra properties supplied to the controller should not bound to the domain object
